HEADWORD: Perigynous
<hw>Pe*rig"y*nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>peri-</ets> + Gr. <?/ woman.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having
